h1. debug

h2. Purpose

Toggles debug logging of the request.

h2. Examples

{code}
new RequestBuilder().post {
    uri = "example.com"
    debug = true
}
{code}

h2. Description

If @true@, the outbound request and the response will be logged, complete with headers and content. Logging is done through log4j in the @com.budjb.requestbuilder@ package name.
